00:00:23.450 --> 00:00:25.160
It's great, okay.

00:00:25.160 --> 00:00:28.670
Welcome. I'm Dr. Curtis
Sandberg and I get

00:00:28.670 --> 00:00:30.200
to have a couple
of minutes here.

