I'm the Director of the David
M. Rubenstein National Center

00:00:33.910 --> 00:00:35.210
for White House History

00:00:35.210 --> 00:00:38.000
at the White House Historical
Association and I'm also --

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:39.370
I have this very long job title.

00:00:39.370 --> 00:00:40.780
I'm also Senior Vice President

00:00:40.780 --> 00:00:42.770
for Educational Resources
